OL,3,CStorm Bert: Rugby club devastated by
OL,4,Cflooding may be forced to close its
OL,5,Cdoors
OL,7,FA rugby club in Caerphilly may be
OL,8,Fforced to close its doors for good
OL,9,Ffollowing severe flooding which left
OL,10,Fthe site submerged in water.
OL,12,FMembers of Cross Keys Rugby Club say
OL,13,Fthey are "more than devastated" after
OL,14,FStorm Bert left in its wake 'thousands
OL,15,Fupon thousands of pounds worth of
OL,16,Fdamages'.
