OL,3,CStorm Bert: Rugby club devastated by
OL,4,Cflooding may be forced to close its
OL,5,Cdoors
OL,7,FColin Vernall, social club chair at
OL,8,FCross Keys rugby club said "no
OL,9,Flessons" have been learned since major
OL,10,Fflooding caused by Storm Dennis
OL,11,Fimpacted the club in 2020.
OL,13,F"It's heartbreaking," he said.
OL,15,F"We've got weddings, we've got
OL,16,FChristmas fetes, we've got lots of
OL,17,Fthings in the club over Christmas,
OL,18,Fjust like any other club. We're going
OL,19,Fto lose thousands and thousands."
