OL,3,CStorm Bert: Rugby club devastated by
OL,4,Cflooding may be forced to close its
OL,5,Cdoors
OL,7,FHe continued: "Without a little bit of
OL,8,Fhelp, the club won't be reopening, and
OL,9,Fthat's being honest. It's just the
OL,10,Fcost of it. It's thousands upon
OL,11,Fthousands to put the club back right."
OL,13,FMr Vernall claimed that despite
OL,14,Freaching out to Caerphilly Council on
OL,15,Fmany occasions to express his concern
OL,16,Fabout flood defences, he never
OL,17,Freceived a reply.
