OL,3,CStorm Bert: Rugby club devastated by
OL,4,Cflooding may be forced to close its
OL,5,Cdoors
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Cymru Wales, he said:
OL,8,F"We could do with a little bit of help
OL,9,Ffrom Caerphilly council to be honest.
OL,10,FLike last time we just haven't seen
OL,11,Fthem and it's disappointing really
OL,12,Fthat we can't get anyone from the
OL,13,Fcouncil to help us here.
OL,15,F"No lessons have been learned from
OL,16,F2020 and I've emailed and spoken to a
OL,17,Fnumber of people regarding this, to
OL,18,Flook for better defences and to be
OL,19,Fhonest I've never ever had one reply,
OL,20,Fnot even from Caerphilly council.
