OL,3,CStorm Bert: Rugby club devastated by
OL,4,Cflooding may be forced to close its
OL,5,Cdoors
OL,7,F"Nobody seems to be interested in it,
OL,8,Fit's just left dead as a doornail.
OL,9,FUnbelievable. This is worse than last
OL,10,Ftime, and nobody has done anything
OL,11,Fabout it. We've had four years to
OL,12,Fthink about it and nothing has
OL,13,Fhappened."
OL,15,FIn response, a Caerphilly County
OL,16,FBorough Council spokesman said: "Storm
OL,17,FBert caused flooding issues across the
OL,18,Fregion as rivers and drainage
OL,19,Finfrastructure struggled to cope with
OL,20,Fthe significant volume of rainfall.
