OL,3,CStorm Bert: Rugby club devastated by
OL,4,Cflooding may be forced to close its
OL,5,Cdoors
OL,7,F"Our teams worked around the clock to
OL,8,Fsupport the community and our thoughts
OL,9,Fgo out to all those whose homes and
OL,10,Fbusinesses have been impacted by
OL,11,Fflooding.
OL,13,F"We are currently considering options
OL,14,Fto provide support to those affected
OL,15,Fand details will be communicated in
OL,16,Fdue course."
