OL,3,CStorm Bert: Rugby club devastated by
OL,4,Cflooding may be forced to close its
OL,5,Cdoors
OL,7,FVolunteers gathered at the club during
OL,8,Fthe days following the flood in order
OL,9,Fto try to mitigate some of the damage
OL,10,Fcaused by the storm, Mr Vernall said:
OL,11,F"We've been working in the club 24/7
OL,12,Fto try to get it up and running.
OL,13,FHopefully we'll try and do one room at
OL,14,Fa time, How long it's going to take
OL,15,Fus, I don't really know... "
