OL,3,CStorm Bert: Rugby club devastated by
OL,4,Cflooding may be forced to close its
OL,5,Cdoors
OL,7,F"The community is really great,
OL,8,Fthey've come to help us again today.
OL,9,FWe'll have people back here tomorrow,
OL,10,Fand without them the club would be
OL,11,Fclosed, there's no doubt about it. The
OL,12,Fcommunity has rallied around us again,
OL,13,Fthey're absolutely fabulous. I
OL,14,Fcouldn't wish for better people."
OL,16,FCross Keys R.F.C was also visited on
OL,17,FMonday, 25 November by Welsh Rugby
OL,18,FUnion CEO Abi Tierney who saw first
OL,19,Fhand the "strength of local community".
